About the meetup group

We are a community of software developers in Wetzlar | Giessen, Germany. Whether you love writing code or are just getting started, you are welcome here!

In Wetzlar and into programing?
You need to join our meetup!

Every 3rd Wednesday of the month you’ll find us talking about what we’re doing and what’s happening around us in the world of programing.
